title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

com.google.android.providers.gsf.permiss.description: Allows an application to modify the Google services map. Not for use by common applications.

android.permission.ACCESS_BACKGROUND_LOC.description: Allows an app to access location in the background. If you're requesting this permission, you must also request either

android.permission.ACTIVITY_RECOGNITION.info: allow application to recognize physical activity
android.permission.ACTIVITY_RECOGNITION.description: Allows an application to recognize physical activity.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "Finding Fast WiFi is important to us because we think it's important to you. We are a small team of four, constantly working on improving SpeedSpot. "IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "Like all developers we pay Google a 30% cut for creating and maintaining the Play Store. Of the remaining 70% we use about two thirds on salaries for our awesome team. The other third goes almost entirely towards paying the server and bandwidth costs as well as the map service providing the offline map tiles. Lastly, we do make a small profit that we use to explore new business opportunities."
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "A good browsing experience is dependent on a low latency (ping) and a high download speed."
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "A download speed of more than 5Mbps with a latency of less than 200ms allows for a smooth browsing experience of content rich websites."
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "A download speed of more than 0.5Mbps with a latency of less then 1000ms allows for a browsing experience with minor delays."
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "A download speed of less than 0.5Mbps or a very high latency might cause serious delays when browsing."
"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "A good email experience is dependent on a high download speed for receiving emails and a high upload speed for sending emails."
"InternetQualityEmailGreen" : "A download/upload speed of more than 5Mbps/1Mbps allows fast handling of large attachments."
"InternetQualityEmailOrange" : "A download/upload speed of more than 0.5Mbps/0.1Mbps allows decent email communication with small attachments."
"InternetQualityEmailRed" : "A download/upload speed of less than 0.5Mbps/0.1Mbps is enough for emails without attachments."
"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "The most relevant factor for gaming is a low latency (ping). Download and upload speeds are secondary."
"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "A latency of less than 100ms combined with a download/upload speed of more than 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps is recommended for a smooth real time online gaming experience."
"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "A latency of less than 300ms combined with a download/upload speed of more than 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps can be enough for casual real time online gaming."
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "A latency of more than 300ms will result in serious delays. This makes real time gaming difficult."

"InternetQualityStreamingDiscription" : "A good streaming experience is only dependent on a high download speed. Netflix asks for a minimum of 0.5Mbps and recommends 25Mbps for Ultra HD, 5Mbps for HD, 3Mbps for SD."
"InternetQualityStreamingGreen" : "A download speed of more than 25Mbps is recommended for ultra high quality streaming."
"InternetQualityStreamingOrange" : "A download speed of more than 5Mbps is recommended for high quality streaming."
"InternetQualityStreamingRed" : "A download speed of less than 5Mbps might result in long buffering times, dependent on the streaming quality."
"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "A good video chat experience is demanding. It depends on a low latency (ping), a high download speed and a high upload speed."
"InternetQualityVideochatGreen" : "A latency of less than 100ms combined with a download/upload speed of more than 4Mbps/4Mbps is recommended for a smooth HD quality video chat experience."
"InternetQualityVideochatOrange" : "A latency of less than 400ms combined with a download/upload speed of more than 1Mbps/1Mbps is enough for most standard video chats."
"InternetQualityVideochatRed" : "A latency of more than 400ms or a download/upload speed of less than 1Mbps/1Mbps might result in long delays or poor video quality."

"philosophy_text" : "

SpeedSpot lets you test the speed of internet connections and more importantly it enables you to share your WiFi test results taken in hotels, cafes, restaurants and many other places with the SpeedSpot Community. That also means it enables all SpeedSpotters to share their results with you. This way you can find the fastest WiFi hotspots anywhere in the world.

Speed matters - because video conferencing, streaming movies or music, sharing photos or videos is no fun when you have a poor internet connection. But, due to poor network coverage and mobile carriers installing increasing amounts of data caps, WiFi will still be the most reliable way to do data intensive tasks over the next few years. So why isn't there a way to find fast WiFi hotspots? I don't know either, but I think there should be. That's why I built SpeedSpot.

"

"privacy_policy_text" : "

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application SpeedSpot (“Application”) for mobile devices that was created by Frederik Lipfert. The Application is a mobile speed test and Wi-Fi finder. With SpeedSpot you can test the speed of cellular and Wi-Fi connections and share information about Wi-Fi hotspots with the SpeedSpot community so SpeedSpot users can find fast Wi-Fi hotspots.

What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?
User Provided Information
No registration is required to use the Application. Automatically Collected Information
The Application may collect certain information automatically, including, but not limited to, the type of mobile device you use, your mobile devices unique device ID, the IP address of your mobile device, your mobile operating system, the type of mobile Internet browsers you use, and information about the way you use the Application.

Does the Application collect precise real time location information of the device?
In order to monitor and improve the speed test algorithm all tests taken are stored, but no personal information is collected and therefore none is stored that connects a test to the SpeedSpot User taking it. The anonymous test results include the ping (ms), download & upload speed (Mbps), the IPv4 or IPv6 network address, the test time, connection type (cellular or Wi-Fi), carrier name and SSID, as well as, if you explicitly allowed location access, the approximate location information. For tests that you choose to add to the Wi-Fi Finder database also the name and the venue type (hotel, cafe, etc.) is collected.
If you do not want us to use your location for the purposes set forth above, you should turn off the location services for the mobile application located in your account settings or in your mobile phone settings and/or within the mobile application.

Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by the Application?
Yes. We will share your information with third parties only in the ways that are described in this privacy statement.
We may disclose User Provided and Automatically Collected Information:
• as required by law, such as to comply with a subpoena, or similar legal process;
• when we believe in good faith that disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, protect your safety or the safety of others, investigate fraud, or respond to a government request;
• with our trusted services providers who work on our behalf, do not have an independent use of the information we disclose to them, and have agreed to adhere to the rules set forth in this privacy statement.
• if Frederik Lipfert is involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of its assets, you will be notified via email and/or a prominent notice on our Web site of any change in ownership or uses of this information, as well as any choices you may have regarding this information.

What are my opt-out rights?
You can stop all collection of information by the Application easily by uninstalling the Application. You may use the standard uninstall processes as may be available as part of your mobile device or via the mobile application marketplace or network.

Data Retention Policy, Managing Your Information
We will retain User Provided data for as long as you use the Application and for a reasonable time thereafter. We will retain Automatically Collected anonymous information and thereafter may store it in aggregate.

Children
We do not use the Application to knowingly solicit data from or market to children under the age of 13. If a parent or guardian becomes aware that his or her child has provided us with information without their consent, he or she should contact us at support@speedspot.org. We will delete such information from our files within a reasonable time.

Security
We are concerned about safeguarding the confidentiality of your information. We provide physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards to protect information we process and maintain. For example, we limit access to this information to authorized employees and contractors who need to know that information in order to operate, develop or improve our Application. Please be aware that, although we endeavor provide reasonable security for information we process and maintain, no security system can prevent all potential security breaches.

Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by updating the Privacy Policy in the Application. You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes. 

Google Analytics
We use Google Analytics to track the number of active users, from where in the world the application is being used, adoption and usage of specific features and crashes and exceptions. All this data is collected anonymously. 

Your Consent
By using the Application, you are consenting to our processing of your information as set forth in this Privacy Policy now and as amended by us. ”Processing”, means using cookies on a computer/hand held device or using or touching information in any way, including, but not limited to, collecting, storing, deleting, using, combining and disclosing information, all of which activities will take place in Germany. If you reside outside Germany your information will be transferred, processed and stored there under German privacy standards.

Contact us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at support@speedspot.org.

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "高速WiFiの検索は私達にとって重要です。それは、あなたにとって重要な事だからです。私達は４人の小さなチームで、日夜SpeedSpotの改善に励んでいます。継続的なソフト開発には、あなたの支援が必要です。もし支援して頂けますと広告を非表示にする事が出来ます。小さなスターバックスコーヒーの３分の１ぐらいの価値が、SpeedSpotにはあると考えて頂けると幸いです^_^。"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "7割を、私達の素晴らしい仲間達の給与として使っています。この素晴らしい仲間達抜きでは、SpeedSpotは存在する事が出来ません。アプリ収入の残りのほぼ全ては、オフラインマップの地図使用料や、サーバー及び帯域使用料に使っています。最後に私達は、新しいビジネスの機会を生み出すという小さな貢献をしています。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "良いブラウジングエクスペリエンスは、少ない待ち時間と速いダウンロード速度によって生み出されます。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "5Mbpsを超えるダウンロード速度かつ200msを下回る反応速度は、コンテンツが豊富なウェブサイトを快適にブラウジングすることを可能にします。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "0.5Mbpsを超えるダウンロード速度かつ1000msを下回る反応速度は、ほんのわずかの遅れに抑えたブラウジングエクスペリエンスを可能にします。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "0.5Mbpsを超えるダウンロード速度かつ高い反応速度の場合、ブラウジング時に大幅な遅れを引き起こす可能性があります。"
"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "良いEメールエクスペリエンスは、メール受信のためのダウンロード速度やメール送信のためのアップロード速度から得ることができます。"
"InternetQualityEmailGreen" : "5Mbps/1Mbpsを超えるアップロード/ダウンロード速度があれば、容量の大きい添付ファイルが付いたメールも高速で処理することができます。"
"InternetQualityEmailOrange" : "0.5Mbps/0.1Mbpsを超えるダウンロード/アップロード速度があれば、容量の少ない添付ファイルが付いたメールのやり取りには十分です。"
"InternetQualityEmailRed" : "0.5Mbps/0.1Mbpsを超えるダウンロード/アップロードスピードがあれば、添付ファイルなしのメール送受信が問題なく行えます。"
"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "ゲームをプレイするためにもっとも大切な要因は、低い反応速度（ping)です。その次にダウンロードとアップロードスピードとなります。"
"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "100ms以下の反応速度と0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps以上のダウンロード/アップロード速度が組み合わせが、リアルタイムのオンラインゲームをプレイするために必要です。"
"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "300ms以下の反応速度と0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps以上のダウンロード/アップロード速度が組み合わせがあれば、シンプルなリアルタイムオンラインゲームには十分でしょう。"
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "300ms以上の反応速度の場合、大幅な遅れを引き起こす恐れがあります。リアルタイムゲームのプレイが困難になる可能性があります。"
"InternetQualityStreamingDiscription" : "良いストリーミングエクスペリエンスは、ダウンロード速度によります。Netflixは最低0.5MbpsそしてUltraHD向けには 25Mbpsを推奨、HD向けには5Mbps、SD向けには3Mbpsを推奨しています。"
"InternetQualityStreamingGreen" : "25Mbpsを超えるダウンロード速度は、最高品質のストリーミングのために必要とされています。"
"InternetQualityStreamingOrange" : "5Mbpsを超えるダウンロード速度は、高品質のストリーミングのために必要とされています。"
"InternetQualityStreamingRed" : "5Mbpsを下回るダウンロード速度は、長いバッファリング時間を引き起こし、ストリーミングの品質に影響を及ぼします。"
"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "良いビデオチャットエクスペリエンスを生み出すには、様々な要因がかかわってきます。低い反応速度(ping),高いダウンロード速度と高いアップロード速度が必要です。"
"InternetQualityVideochatGreen" : "100msを下回る反応速度と4Mbps/4Mbpsを超えるダウンロード/アップロード速度は、快適なHD品質のビデオチャットのために必要とされています。"
"InternetQualityVideochatOrange" : "400msを下回る反応速度と、1Mbps/1Mbpsを上回るダウンロード/アップロード速度があれば、通常のビデオチャットには十分でしょう。"
"InternetQualityVideochatRed" : "400msを下回る反応速度と、1Mbps/1Mbpsを上回るダウンロード/アップロード速度があれば、通常のビデオチャットには十分でしょう。"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "Schnelles WLAN ist wichtig für uns weil wir glauben dass es wichtig ist für alle. Wir sind ein kleines Team bestehend aus vier Leuten und arbeiten ständig daran SpeedSpot zu verbessern. Falls du die Entwicklung unterstützen möchtest freuen wir uns wenn du für die Entfernung der Werbung bezahlst. Um SpeedSpot weiterzuentwickeln helfen uns auch die kleinen Beträge - ist ja auch nicht teuerer als ein Drittel eines Kaffee beim Starbucks :-)."

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "Wie alle Entwickler zahlen wir 30% an Google für die Nutzung des Play Stores. Von den übrigen 70% zahlen wir ungefähr zwei Drittel an Gehältern für unser großartiges Team aus. Ohne sie würde es SpeedSpot in seiner jetzigen Form nicht geben. Mit dem letzten Drittel begleichen wir fast die gesamten Server und Bandbreitenkosten und bezahlen den Offlinekartenanbieter vom dem wir das Kartenmaterial lizenzieren. Den kleinen Gewinn der letztendlich übrig bleibt nutzen wir zur Entwicklung neuer Funktionen."
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "Ein gutes Surferlebnis benötigt eine niedrige Latenzzeit (Ping) und eine hohe Downloadgeschwindigkeit."
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "Eine Downloadgeschwindigkeit von über 5Mbps mit einer Latenzzeit von unter 200ms garantiert flüssiges Surfen von Websiten mit medialen Inhalten."
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "Eine Downloadgeschwindigkeit von über 0.5Mbps mit einer Latenzzeit von unter 1000ms erlaubt normales Surfen mit kleinen Verzögerungen."
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "Eine Downloadgeschwindigkeit von unter 0.5Mbps oder einer sehr hohe Latenzzeit schränken das Surferlebnis deutlich ein."
"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "Ein gutes Email Erlebnis benötigt eine hohe Downloadgeschwindigkeit um Emails zu empfangen und eine hohe Uploadgeschwindigkeit um Emails zu versenden."
"InternetQualityEmailGreen" : "Eine Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von über 5Mbps/1Mbps erlaubt den problemlosen Umgang mit großen Dateianhängen."
"InternetQualityEmailOrange" : "Eine Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von über 0.5Mbps/0.1Mbps erlaubt den problemlosen Umgang mit Emails und kleinen Dateianhängen."
"InternetQualityEmailRed" : "Eine Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von unter 0.5Mbps/0.1Mbps reicht für normalen Emailverkehr ohne Dateianhänge aus."
"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "Die wichtigste Eigenschaft für Onlinespiele ist eine niedrige Latenzzeit (Ping). Download- und Uploadgeschwindigkeit sind zweitrangig."
"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "Eine Latenzzeit von unter 100ms kombiniert mit einer Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von über 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps wird für ein ruckelfreies Echtzeiterlebnis empfohlen."
"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "Eine Latenzzeit von unter 300ms kombiniert mit einer Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von über 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps kann für das gelegentliche Onlinespiel ausreichen."
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "Eine Latenzzeit von über 300ms führt zu deutlichen Verzögerungen. Damit sind Echtzeitspiele fast unspielbar."

"InternetQualityStreamingDiscription" : "Ein gutes Streamingerlebnis benötigt in erster Linie eine hohe Downloadgeschwindigkeit. Netflix fordert z.B. eine minimale Geschwindigkeit von 0.5Mbps aber empfiehlt 25Mbps für Ultra HD, 5Mbps für HD und 3Mbps für SD."
"InternetQualityStreamingGreen" : "Eine Downloadgeschwindigkeit von über 25Mbps wird für Ultra HD Streaming empfohlen."
"InternetQualityStreamingOrange" : "Eine Downloadgeschwindigkeit von über 5Mbps wird für HD Streaming empfohlen."
"InternetQualityStreamingRed" : "Eine Downloadgeschwindigkeit von unter 5Mbps kann zu langen Lade- und Pufferzeiten führen."

"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "Ein gutes Video-Chat Erlebnis hat hohe Ansprüche. Dazu sind eine niedrige Latenzzeit (Ping), eine hohe Downloadgeschwindigkeit und eine hohe Uploadgeschwindigkeit nötig."

"InternetQualityVideochatGreen" : "Eine Latenzzeit von weniger als 100ms in Kombination mit einer Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von mehr als 4Mbps/4Mbps wird für ein reibungslosen HD Video-Chat empfohlen."
"InternetQualityVideochatOrange" : "Eine Latenzzeit von weniger als 400ms in Kombination mit einer Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von mehr als 1Mbps/1Mbps reicht für die meisten Video-Chats aus."

"InternetQualityVideochatRed" : "Eine Latenzzeit von mehr als 400ms oder eine Download-/Uploadgeschwindigkeit von weniger als 1Mbps/1Mbps kann zu Aussetzern, Verzögerungen und schlechter Videoqualität führen."

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "找到快速的WiFi对于我们非常重要因为我们认为这对你们非常重要。我们是一个非常小的团队，目前只有四个人，正在不断坚持提高SpeedSpot这款软件的性能。如果你们想支持这种坚持不懈的长期开发工作，你们可以考虑支付一些费用给我们来去除软件中的广告。希望你考虑使用SpeedSpot这款软件，购买它的费用仅仅相当于喝一杯小号星巴克咖啡的三分之一:-)。"
"IAP_RemoveAds_Text2" : "当你付款%1$s给SpeedSpot的时候，你的钱去哪里了？"
"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "三分之二是用来支付团队成员的工资。团队中的每个成员都是SpeedSpot软件可以存在的重要因素；另外的三分之一几乎用来支付服务器，带宽以及离线地图下载所带来的费用。最后剩下来的微小利润，我们用来去开拓更多的商业机会。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "要享受高效网站浏览体验，用户应尽量缩短反应时间（延时）和提升下载速度。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "如下载速度高于 5Mbps 而反应时间低于 200ms，用户可流畅浏览内容丰富的网站。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "如下载速度高于 0.5Mbps 而反应时间低于 1000ms，用户的网页浏览体验也许会有轻微延迟。"
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "如下载速度低于 0.5Mbps 而且反应时间非常高，浏览网站时可能会出现严重延迟。"
"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "高效电邮通信的首要条件是用户能透过高速下载/上传收发电邮。"
"InternetQualityEmailGreen" : "如下载/上传速度高于 5Mbps/1Mbps，用户能快速处理大型附件。"
"InternetQualityEmailOrange" : "如下载/上传速度高于 0.5Mbps/0.1Mb​​ps，用户可有效处理带有小型附件的电邮通信。"
"InternetQualityEmailRed" : "如下载/上传速度低于 0.5Mbps/0.1Mb​​ps，用户仍可处理不带附件的电邮。"
"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "电脑游戏所讲求的是较短的反应时间（延时）。下载和上传速度都只是次要。"
"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "如反应时间低于 100ms 而下载/上传速度高于 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps，用户可享受流畅无阻的实时线上游戏体验。"
"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "如反应时间低于 300ms 而下载/上传速度高于 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps ，可能已足够进行一般实时线上游戏。"
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "如反应时间超过 300ms，则会导致严重延迟，用户很难流畅进行实时游戏。"
"InternetQualityStreamingDiscription" : "串流媒体只讲求高速下载能力。 Netflix 的最低速度要求为 0.5Mbps；超高清画质建议速度为 25Mbps；高清画质建议有 5Mbps；而标清画质则只要求 3Mbps。"
"InternetQualityStreamingGreen" : "如想享受超高品质的媒体串流，建议有高于 25Mbps 的下载速度。"
"InternetQualityStreamingOrange" : "如想享受高品质的媒体串流，建议有高于 5Mbps 的下载速度。"
"InternetQualityStreamingRed" : "低于 5Mbps 的下载速度可能会导致漫长的缓冲时间，实际时间取决于串流质量。"
"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "流畅无阻的视频聊天体验有很高的配置要求，需要很低的反应时间（延时）和高速下载/上传能力。"
"InternetQualityVideochatGreen" : "如反应时间低于 100ms 而下载/上传速度高于 4Mbps/4Mbps，用户可享受流畅的高清视频聊天体验。"
"InternetQualityVideochatOrange" : "如反应时间低于 400ms 而下载/上传速度达到 1Mbps/1Mbps，用户可进行最标准规格的视频聊天。"
"InternetQualityVideochatRed" : "如反应时间超过 400 ms 或下载/上传速度低于1Mbps/1Mbps，则可能导致严重延时或较差的视频质量。"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "सभी डेवलपरों की तरह हम गूगल को प्ले स्टोर को बनाने और मैंटेन करने के लिए 30% भुगतान करते हैं। बाकी बचे 70% की दो तिहाई को हम अपने जबर्दस्त टीम के वेतन पर खर्च करते हैं। स्पीडस्पॉट उनके बिना अपने वर्तमान रूप में नहीं होता। बाकी बचे एक तिहाई को हम सर्वर और बैंडविड्थ लागतों के साथ-साथ ऑफलाइन मैप टैल प्रदान करने वाली मानचित्र सेवाओं पर खर्च करते हैं। अंततः, हम कुछ मुनाफा भी कमाते हैं जिसका प्रयोग हम नई व्यावसायिक मौकों को खोजने के लिए करते हैं।"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text2" : "Là où votre argent part lorsque vous payez %1$s à SpeedSpot"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "Comme tous les développeurs, nous payons une part de 30% à Apple pour la création et le maintien de l'App Store. Sur les 70% restants, nous investissons environ les deux tiers dans les salaires de notre équipe fantastique. SpeedSpot ne pourrait pas exister sous sa forme actuelle sans eux. Le dernier tiers sert presque entièrement à payer le serveur et les frais de bande passante ainsi que le service de carte qui nous fournit les cartes hors ligne. Enfin, nous faisons un petit bénéfice dont nous nours servons afin d'explorer de nouvelles opportunités de commerce."
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "Une bonne expérience de navigation est tributaire d’une faible latence (ping) et une vitesse de téléchargement élevée."

"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "Le facteur le plus pertinent pour les jeux est un faible temps de latence (ping). Download et upload des vitesses sont secondaires."

"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "Une latence de moins de 100ms combinée avec une vitesse de téléchargement de plus de 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps est recommandé pour une expérience de jeu en ligne en temps réel sans heurt."

"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "Une latence de moins de 300 ms combinée avec une vitesse de téléchargement de plus de 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps peut être suffisant pour les jeux en ligne occasionnels en temps réel."
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "Un temps de latence de plus de 300ms se traduira par des retards. Cela rend le jeu en temps réel difficile."

"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "Une expérience de bonne conversation vidéo est exigeant. Il repose sur une faible latence (ping), une vitesse de téléchargement élevée et une vitesse de téléchargement."

"GDPR_Text1" : "Esperamos que disfrutes usando Speedcheck tanto como nosotros disfrutamos haciéndolo - pero es un servicio caro de ejecutar debido a costes muy altos de ancho de banda y servidor. "IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "Encontrar WiFi Rápido es importante para nosotros porque creemos que es importante para ti. Somos un equipo pequeño de cuatro personas, trabajando constantemente en mejorar SpeedSpot. Si quieres apoyar el desarrollo continuo puedes hacerlo pagando por la eliminación de los anuncios. Con suerte te darás cuenta de la utilidad de SpeedSpot y que vale la pena por el precio de un café pequeño del Starbucks Coffee :-)."
"IAP_RemoveAds_Text2" : "Dónde va tu dinero cuando pagas %1$s a SpeedSpot"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "Como todos los desarrolladores pagamos a Apple un 30% para la creación y el mantenimiento de la App Store. Del 70% restante, utilizamos sobre dos tercios en los salarios de nuestro equipo increíble. SpeedSpot no podría existir tal y como es ahora sin ellos. El otro tercio está destinado casi por completo a pagar los costes del servidor y del ancho de banda así como en proporcionar los fragmentos de los mapas. Finalmente, conseguimos un pequeño beneficio que utilizamos en explorar nuevas oportunidades de negocios."
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "Una buena experiencia de navegación depende de una baja latencia (ping) y una velocidad de descarga alta."
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "Una velocidad de descarga de más de 5Mbps con una latencia inferior a 200ms permite una experiencia de navegación fluida en sitios web ricos en contenido."
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "Una velocidad de descarga de más de 0,5Mbps con una latencia inferior a 1000ms permite una experiencia de navegación con pequeños retrasos."
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "Una velocidad de descarga de menos de 0,5Mbps o una latencia muy alta puede causar serios retrasos a la hora de navegar."

"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "Una buena experiencia de correo electrónico depende de una velocidad de descarga para recibir correos electrónicos y una alta velocidad de carga para enviar correos electrónicos."
"InternetQualityEmailGreen" : "Una velocidad de subida/descarga de más de 5Mbps/1Mbps permite la manipulación rápida de adjuntos de gran tamaño."
"InternetQualityEmailOrange" : "Una velocidad de subida/descarga de más de 0,5Mbps/0,1Mbps permite una comunicación decente de correos electrónicos con adjuntos de pequeño tamaño."
"InternetQualityEmailRed" : "Una velocidad de subida/descarga de menos de 0,5Mbps/0,1Mbps es suficiente para correos electrónicos sin archivos adjuntos."
"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "El factor más relevante para los juegos es una baja latencia (ping). Las velocidades de subida y descarga son secundarias."
"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "Una latencia inferior a 100ms combinado con una velocidad de subida/descarga de más de 0,5Mbps/0,5Mbps está recomendada para una experiencia fluida de juego en línea."
"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "Una latencia inferior a 300ms combinada con una velocidad de subida/descarga de más de 0,5Mbps/0,5Mbps puede ser suficiente para juegos normales en línea."
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "Una latencia de más de 300ms proporcionará serios retrasos. Esto hace difícil jugar en tiempo real."

"InternetQualityStreamingDiscription" : "Una buena experiencia de retransmisión solo depende de una alta velocidad de descarga. Netflix pide una velocidad mínima de 0,5Mbps y recomienda 25Mbps para Ultra HD, 5Mbps para HD y 3Mbps para SD."
"InternetQualityStreamingGreen" : "Una velocidad de descarga superior a 25Mbps es recomendada para una retransmisión de calidad ultra"
"InternetQualityStreamingOrange" : "Una velocidad de descarga superior a 5Mbps es recomendada para una retransmisión de alta calidad."
"InternetQualityStreamingRed" : "Una velocidad de descarga inferior a 5Mbps puede requerir largos periodos de carga, dependientes de la calidad de retransmisión."
"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "Una buena experiencia de chat en vídeo es exigente. Depende de una baja latencia (ping), y una velocidad de subida y descarga altas."

"InternetQualityVideochatGreen" : "Una latencia inferior a 100ms combinada con una velocidad de subida/descarga de más de 4Mbps/4Mbps es recomendada para una buena experiencia de calidad de vídeo HD."
"InternetQualityVideochatOrange" : "Una latencia inferior a 400ms combinada con una velocidad de subida/descarga de más de 1Mbps/1Mbps es suficiente para la mayoría de chats en vídeo estándar."
"InternetQualityVideochatRed" : "Una latencia superior a 400ms o una velocidad de subida/descarga inferior a 1Mbps/1Mbps puede ocasionar retrasos prolongados o una mala calidad de vídeo."

"GDPR_Text1" : "Ci auguriamo che l'utilizzo di Speedcheck ti stia piacendo almeno quanto è piaciuto a noi realizzarlo, ma a causa degli elevati costi per i server e la larghezza di banda, la gestione del Servizio è molto dispendiosa. "IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "Individuare punti d'accesso Wi-Fi è importante per noi perché sappiamo quanto lo sia per te. Siamo un piccolo gruppo di quattro programmatori, costantemente al lavoro per migliorare SpeedSpot. Se vuoi supportare i continui miglioramenti, puoi contribuire pagando appena la rimozione della pubblicità. Sicuramente riterrai che valga la pena di usufruire dell'utilità di SpeedSpot ad un terzo del prezzo di un caffè da Starbucks :-)."
"IAP_RemoveAds_Text2" : "A cosa viene destinato il tuo denaro quando paghi %1$s a SpeedSpot"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "Come tutti gli sviluppatori noi paghiamo alla Apple una commissione di manutenzione del 30%. Utilizziamo circa due terzi del restante 70% per pagare i salari al nostro eccellente team. SpeedSpot non potrebbe aver raggiunto i risultati attuali senza il loro apporto. L'ultimo terzo è destinato quasi interamente al pagamento del server e ai costi della larghezza di banda e del servizio delle mappe volto a fornire le indicazioni offline. Infine, il minimo profitto restante lo utilizziamo per sperimentare nuove opportunità commerciali."
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "Una buona esperienza di navigazione dipende da una bassa latenza (ping) e da un'alta velocità di download."
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "Una velocità di download superiore a 5Mbps con una latenza inferiore a 200ms permette un'ottima esperienza di navigazione su siti internet ricchi di contenuti."
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "Una velocità di download superiore a 0.5Mbps con una latenza inferiore a 1000ms permette un'esperienza di navigazione con ritardi minori."
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "Una velocità di download inferiore a 0.5Mbps con una latenza molto alta potrebbe causare dei seri ritardi durante la navigazione."
"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "Un buon servizio di email dipende da un'alta velocità di download e upload per ricevere e inviare email."
"InternetQualityEmailGreen" : "Una velocità di download/upload superiore a 5Mbps/1Mbps permette di gestire velocemente allegati di grandi dimensioni."
"InternetQualityEmailOrange" : "Una velocità di download/upload superiore a 0.5Mbps/0.1Mbps permette una buona comunicazione email e la gestione di allegati di piccole dimensioni."
"InternetQualityEmailRed" : "Una velocità di download/upload inferiore a 0.5Mbps/0.1Mbps permette l'invio di email senza allegati."
"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "Il fattore rilevante quando si gioca è un bassa latenza. Velocità di download e upload sono fattori secondari."
"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "Una latenza inferiore a 100ms insieme ad una velocità di download superiore a 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps è consigliata per un'ottima esperienza di gioco online in tempo reale."

"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "Una latenza inferiore a 300ms insieme ad una velocità di download/upload superiore a 0.5Mbps/0.5Mbps può essere sufficiente per una buona esperienza di gioco online in tempo reale."
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "Una latenza superiore a 300ms causerà seri ritardi. Ciò renderà difficile giocare online in tempo reale."

"InternetQualityStreamingDiscription" : "Una buona esperienza di streaming dipende esclusivamente da un'alta velocità di download. Netflix richiede almeno 0.5Mbps e consiglia 25Mbps per l'Ultra HD, 5Mbps per l'HD, 3Mbps per SD."
"InternetQualityStreamingGreen" : "Una velocità di download superiore a 25Mbps è consigliata per una qualità di streaming molto elevata."
"InternetQualityStreamingOrange" : "Una velocità di download superiore a 5Mbps è consigliata per un'alta qualità di streaming."
"InternetQualityStreamingRed" : "Una velocità di download inferiore a 5Mbps potrebbe causare problemi di buffering, a seconda della qualità di streaming."
"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "Una buona esperienza di video chat è difficoltosa. Dipende da una bassa latenza (ping) e da un'alta velocità di download/upload."

"InternetQualityVideochatGreen" : "Una latenza inferiore a 100ms insieme ad una velocità di download/upload superiore a 4Mbps/4Mbps è consigliata per un'ottima esperienza di chat con qualità video HD."
"InternetQualityVideochatOrange" : "Una latenza inferiore a 400ms insieme ad una velocità di download/upload superiore a 1Mbps/1Mbps è sufficiente per la maggior parte delle video chat standard."
"InternetQualityVideochatRed" : "Una latenza superiore a 400ms o una velocità di download/upload inferiore a 1Mbps/1Mbps potrebbe causare lunghi ritardi o una scarsa qualità video."

"GDPR_Text1" : "Esperamos que goste tanto de utilizar o Speedcheck quanto nós gostamos de o fazer. Por conseguinte, subsidiamos o serviço ao recolher e partilhar IDs de anúncios e dados de localização com terceiros selecionados que utilizam os dados para lhe apresentar apenas anúncios relevantes."

"GDPR_Text2" : "Ao aceitar, permite que nós e os nossos parceiros processemos e armazenemos os seus dados para os fins descritos acima. Para obter mais detalhes, consulte a nossa Política de Privacidade. Se você tem menos de 16 anos, deve perguntar aos seus pais ou guardião."

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "Encontrar WiFi Rápida é importante para nós porque pensamos que é importante para ti. Somos uma pequena equipa de quatro pessoas, a trabalhar constantemente para melhorar o SpeedSpot. Se queres contribuir para o desenvolvimento contínuo podes fazê-lo pagando pela remoção dos anúncios. Esperamos que consideres que a utilidade do SpeedSpot valha um terço do preço de um café pequeno no Starbucks :-)."
"IAP_RemoveAds_Text2" : "Para onde vai o teu dinheiro quando pagas %1$s ao SpeedSpot"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "Tal como todos os desenvolvedores pagamos à Apple 30% pela criação e manutenção da App Store. Dos restantes 70% usamos cerca de dois terços para os salários da nossa incrível equipa. SpeedSpot não poderia existir tal como é hoje sem eles. O restante terço serve quase na totalidade para pagar os custos do servidor e de banda larga, assim como o fornecimento dos fragmentos de mapas pelo serviço de mapas. Por último, conseguimos um pouco de lucro que usamos para explorar novas oportunidades de negócio."
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "Uma boa experiência de navegação está dependente de uma baixa latência (ping) e de uma alta velocidade de download."
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "Uma velocidade de download de mais de 5 Mbps com uma latência de menos de 200ms permite uma experiência de navegação suave em sites ricos em conteúdo."
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "Uma velocidade de download de mais de 0.5Mbps com uma latência de menos de 1,000 ms permite uma experiência de navegação com pequenos atrasos."
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "Uma velocidade de download de menos de 0.5Mbps ou uma latência muito alta pode causar sérios atrasos durante a navegação."
"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "Uma boa experiência de e-mail está dependente de uma alta velocidade de download para receber e-mails e uma alta velocidade de upload para o envio de e-mails."
"InternetQualityEmailGreen" : "A velocidade de download / upload de mais de 5 Mbps / 1 Mbps permite um manuseamento rápido de anexos volumosos."

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text1" : "Поиск скоростного Wi-Fi очень важен для нас, поскольку мы считаем, что он нужен вам. Мы являемся небольшой командой из четырех человек, которая постоянно работает над улучшением SpeedSpot. Если вы хотите поддержать развитие проекта, то это можно сделать, заплатив за удаление рекламы. Обратите внимание на полезность данных SpeedSpot, стоимость которых составляет всего треть от цены небольшой кружки кофе в Starbucks:-)."
"IAP_RemoveAds_Text2" : "Куда уходят ваши деньги, когда вы тратите %1$s на SpeedSpot"

"IAP_RemoveAds_Text3" : "Как и все разработчики, мы отдаем компании Apple 30% дохода для создания и поддержания App Store. Из оставшихся 70% примерно две трети уходят на заработную плату нашей команды. SpeedSpot не смог бы существовать в текущей форме без их помощи. Остаток практически полностью уходит на оплату расходов, связанных с сервером, хостингом, а также картографическим сервисом, обеспечивающим бесперебойную работу карт. В результате, мы получаем совсем небольшую прибыль, которую используем для исследования новых возможностей для бизнеса."
"InternetQualityBrowsingDiscription" : "Хорошая навигация по Интернету зависит от низкой латентности (пингования) и высокой скорости загрузки."
"InternetQualityBrowsingGreen" : "Скорость загрузки более 5 Мбит с латентностью менее 200 мс обеспечивает плавную навигацию по веб-сайтам с богатым контентом."
"InternetQualityBrowsingOrange" : "Скорость загрузки более 0,5 Мбит с латентностью менее 1000 мс обеспечивает навигацию по веб-сайтам с минимальными задержками."
"InternetQualityBrowsingRed" : "Скорость загрузки менее 0,5 Мбит или высокая латентность приводят к длительным задержкам при навигации по Интернету."
"InternetQualityEmailDiscription" : "Хорошая работа электронной почты зависит от высокой скорости скачивания для получения сообщений и высокой скорости загрузки для их отправки."

"InternetQualityEmailOrange" : "Скорость скачивания/загрузки более 0,5 Мбит/0,1 Мбит позволяет поддерживать связь с небольшими вложениями."
"InternetQualityEmailRed" : "Скорость скачивания/загрузки менее 0,5 Мбит/0,1 Мбит подходит лишь для использования электронной почты без вложений."
"InternetQualityGamingDiscription" : "Наиболее важным фактором для игр в режиме онлайн является низкая латентность (пинг). Скорость скачивания и загрузки являются вторичными."
"InternetQualityGamingGreen" : "Для игр в режиме онлайн рекомендуется латентность менее 100 мс, в сочетании со скоростью скачивания/загрузки более 0,5 Мбит / 0,5 Мбит."
"InternetQualityGamingOrange" : "Для простых игр в режиме онлайн рекомендуется латентность менее 300 мс, в сочетании со скоростью скачивания/загрузки более 0,5 Мбит / 0,5 Мбит."
"InternetQualityGamingRed" : "Латентость более 300 мс приводит к серьезным задержкам в соединении. Это делает игру в режиме онлайн практически невозможной."

"InternetQualityStreamingDiscription" : "Хороший стриминг зависит только от высокой скорости скачивания. Netflix требует как минимум 0,5 Мбит и рекомендует 25 Мбит для Ultra HD, 5 Мбит для HD, 3Мбит для SD."

"InternetQualityStreamingOrange" : "Для высокого качества потокового видео рекомендована скорость скачивания более 5 Мбит."
"InternetQualityStreamingRed" : "Скорость скачивания менее 5 Мбит может привести к увеличению времени буферизации,что зависит от качества потоковой передачи."
"InternetQualityVideochatDiscription" : "Качественный видео-чат довольно требователен. Он зависит от низкой латентности (пинга), высокой скорости скачивания и загрузки."
"InternetQualityVideochatGreen" : "Для плавного HD-изображения в видео-чате рекомендуется латентность менее 100 мс, в сочетании со скоростью скачивания/загрузки более 4 Мбит / 4 Мбит."
"InternetQualityVideochatOrange" : "Для большинства видео-чатов достаточно латентности менее 400 мс, в сочетании со скоростью скачивания/загрузки более 1 Мбит / 1 Мбит."

playstore_details.title: SPEEDCHECK Internet Speed Test
playstore_details.description:
Use Speedcheck to easily run an internet speed test and measure your internet performance by taking a free cellular or wifi speed test. The automatic check feature even gives you the ability to schedule periodic speed tests to monitor your internet speed continually.
However, simply measuring speed isn't that helpful if you don't know what the results are telling you. To make your internet speed easier to understand we give you a simple overview of how important internet services like email, web surfing, gaming, video streaming or chatting will perform for you.
To provide the best internet speed meter that can reliably test every type and speed of internet connection, we have upgraded our entire server network to 10Gbps connections.
Speedcheck can be used either as an internet speed meter for your cellular connections ( LTE, 4G, 3G) or a wifi analyzer to perform a wifi speed test for wifi hotspots. 

* Test your download and upload speed and latency (ping)
* LTE speed test: Check the speed of your mobile carrier
* WiFi speed test: Analyze the internet speed of your WiFi hotspot, your net, and ISP
* Schedule automatic checks to monitor your connection over time, for example, if you are experiencing issues around a certain time of day you can schedule a speed check to run multiple tests during this particular time window.
* Check and verify if your internet service provider is delivering on its service promise
* Keep track of all your past speed tests and measurements with our intuitive test history along with detailed overviews for every test taken.
* We make it easy for you to share your tests with your friends and followers on social media with a custom image for each speed test

Download the free Speedcheck app for the best, easiest and most reliable way to run an internet speed test and monitor network connection quality and performance for all your internet connections. 

If you experience any issue, have questions or suggestions, we are happy to help. Just send us an email to android@etrality.com
